quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  46,21,"Janto fii musi…ó…ďe Aadi (Huudi) …ďen, nde o jertinirnoo yim…ďe makko …ďen aynde nden - gom…óii hari jertinooji yawtiino yeeso makko e …ďaawo makko - wonnde: \"Wata on rewu si wanaa Allah. Min mi…óo hulani on lepte √Īalaande mawnde"
  46,22,"∆Āe wi'i: \"E a aru men fii yo a firliaa men e rewetee- …ói amen …óin? Awa addan men ko kammbiran…óaa men kon, si wonii ko a jeyaa…óo e goongu…ďe …ďen"
  46,23,"O maaki: \"Ganndal ngal ko ka Allah woni. Min mi yottinanay on tun woni, ko mi nulaa kon. Ko woni tun mi yi'ii ko on yim…ďe majjaa…ďe"
  46,24,"Nde …ďe yi'unoo ruulde honde wee…ďitii fewtiri ay…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe wi'i: \"Ndee ko duulere to…ďaynde e men\". Ko nden kan woni ! ko hawjirno…óon kon : ko henndu, ndu lepte muusu…óe woni e mun"
  46,25,"hindu muncira kala huunde, yamiroore Joomi mayru\". ∆Āe wa…ótini, tawi yi'etaake si wanaa ko…óooli ma…ď…ďe …óin. Ko wano nii Men yo…ďitirta yim…ďe bonnoo…ďe …ďen"
  46,26,"Gom…óii Men ye…óiino …ďe, e kon ko Men ye…óaali on e mun. Men wa…óani …ďe nan…óe, e gii…óe e …ďer…óe. Kono …óen nan…óe ma…ď…ďe, e gii…óe ma…ď…ďe e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe (fow) duncanaali …ďe go…ó…óum, tawde …ďe laatino yeddoo…ďe Aayeeje Allah …óen. Ko …ďe jalkitaynoo kon jippii e ma…ď…ďe"